"     Patient information: Granulomatosis with polyangiitis (Wegener&rsquo;s) (The Basics)",
"    </div>",
"    <span class=\"view\">",
"     View in",
"     <a class=\"lang\" href=\"./es-419/granulomatosis-with-polyangiitis-wegeners-the-basics?source=topic_page\">",
